程序包 dao.mappers

类 User

java.lang.Object
dao.mappers.User
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable
@Alias("User") public class User extends Object implements Serializable
The type User. This class represents a User entity with properties such as user ID, user name, password, and VIP status. It provides methods to get and set these properties. The user ID is generated randomly.

He Chenyi
